(14, 1, '2015-03-10 12:27:22', '2015-03-10 12:27:22', '<div class="row">\n <div class="col-lg-12">\n                    <h2>WEDDING PLANNING SERVICES</h2>\n                    <hr class="star-primary">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        <div class="row">\n      <div class="col-md-12"><p class="wht-fnt">Our wedding planning services include an array of expertise, skills, and experience in order to ensure the entire wedding planning process runs smoothly. Our services can range from helping you find the perfect wedding venue for your wedding, to booking your vendors, to executing your vision on the day-of your wedding. Below are descriptions of Planning Elegance’s three main packages that cover all the aspects of the wedding planning process – we often customize packages to cater to the couples’ specific needs, so contact us today to start creating your perfect day!</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n<div id="portfolio">\n            <div class="row">\n            	<div class="services">\n                <div class="col-sm-6 portfolio-item">\n                    <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/s1.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="">\n                    <h4 class="text-center h4bg">My Elegant Three Month Package</h4>\n                    <div class="serv-txt text-center"><p>This “Month-of-Coordination” package is specially created for couples who already have the big things set for their wedding and just need coordination when it comes closer to their wedding day. With this option, you can get full wedding coordination for up to 90 days before your wedding. This method is strongly preferred to “Day-of-Coordination” so that your coordinator can be fully prepared for your wedding day.</p>\n <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button">Request a free quote today!</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div><div class="col-sm-6 portfolio-item"><img src="[php snippet=1]/images/s2.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt=""><h4 class="text-ce