(63, 1, '2015-03-10 06:26:28', '2015-03-10 06:26:28', ' <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/Fusion-Wedding1.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Interracial weddings are unique in their own special way due to the different aspects of each type of background, culture, and/or religion. When one wedding holds two cultures there are so many interesting details and ceremonies that come together. Interracial marriages at first were not of law and were looked down upon in various cultures. Women who chose to marry someone outside of their religion were banned from getting married. This took place in countries such as Germany, South Africa, and the Arab Nations. Today, fusion weddings and interracial marriages are seen as normal weddings just with a small twist, they are generally exciting and very common in melting pot countries like the United States, England, and Canada.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Fusion Weddings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fusion-weddings', '', '', '2015-03-10 06:38:49', '2015-03-10 06:38:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/planningelegance/?page_id=63', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(64, 1, '2015-03-10 06:26:28', '2015-03-10 06:26:28', ' <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/Fusion-Wedding1.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Interracial weddings are unique in their own special way due to the different aspects of each type of background, culture, and/or religion. When one wedding holds two cultures there are so many interesting details and ceremonies that come together. Interracial marriages at first were not of law and were looked down upon in various cultures. Women who chose to marry someone outside of their religion were banned from getting married. This took place in countries such as Germany, South Africa, and the Arab Nations. Today, fusion weddings and interracial marriages are seen as normal weddings just with a small twist, they are generally exciting and very common in melting pot countries like the United States, England, and Canada.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Fusion Weddings', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-10 06:26:28', '2015-03-10 06:26:28', '', 63, 'http://localhost/planningelegance/?p=64', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
