(81, 1, '2015-03-10 08:46:41', '2015-03-10 08:46:41', '  <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/indian_wedding.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Planning Elegance will make this celebration of bonding two families together unique, traditional, and memorable.  We can adjust to your individual style and taste since every South Asian Wedding is a blend of cultures and each family has their own traditions.  If you are interested in hiring a wedding coordinator, you can set up a FREE consultation meeting with one of our experienced South Asian coordinators.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Our goal is to provide you with all of the resources you need in one place.  The South Asian population in  California is growing everyday – and so are we!  Planning Elegance serves all of California with 2 convenient offices in the City of Orange and San Francisco.  Since the representation for wedding vendors that specialize in South Asian weddings is minimal, hiring a coordinator helps you choose the best vendors in your area and can ease your wedding planning experience.  We are happy to adjust packages to your budget and meet your needs, so contact us today to see how we can help you.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Indian Wedding Planner', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'indian-wedding-planner', '', '', '2015-03-10 08:46:41', '2015-03-10 08:46:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/planningelegance/?page_id=81', 0, 'page', '', 0),
