(83, 1, '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '<div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/our.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">With the countless weddings we have helped coordinate we know there is always room for something new and exciting! That is why the girls at Planning Elegance research and keep up-to-date on the latest trends in the wedding industry, so we can offer you innovative ideas to set your wedding apart from the rest. We want your day to be designed especially for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">You have been planning and dreaming about this day since you were a child. We want to take those dreams and help turn them into a reality! The entire Planning Elegance team will take in your ideas, concerns and questions to help execute the wedding of your dreams. We want this day to be a day that you will never forget!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Our Culture & Mission', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-culture-mission', '', '', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/planningelegance/?page_id=83', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(85, 1, '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '<div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/our.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">With the countless weddings we have helped coordinate we know there is always room for something new and exciting! That is why the girls at Planning Elegance research and keep up-to-date on the latest trends in the wedding industry, so we can offer you innovative ideas to set your wedding apart from the rest. We want your day to be designed especially for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">You have been planning and dreaming about this day since you were a child. We want to take those dreams and help turn them into a reality! The entire Planning Elegance team will take in your ideas, concerns and questions to help execute the wedding of your dreams. We want this day to be a day that you will never forget!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Our Culture & Mission', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '2015-03-10 11:57:07', '', 83, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?p=85', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(86, 1, '2015-03-10 12:05:25', '2015-03-10 12:05:25', '<div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/destination.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Wedding planners take on many different forms like books, internet articles, websites, and people.  Of course, you’re planning your wedding on a budget and hiring a person to plan your wedding is not the most affordable option, but it could be the most practical.  Learn why you might need a wedding planner to help you plan your wedding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Our job entails several different aspects, but mainly we do everything in our power to make sure our clients are 100% happy with everything.  To sum up, we bring your dream wedding to reality!  Planning Elegance wedding professionals will help you with every detail of your wedding from scheduling meetings for you to searching for the most unique vendor to cramming everything you want into your budget to being there for you throughout your entire wedding day.  We are your managers, your assistants, your designers, your advisers, and most of all, your piece of mind.  Wedding planners guarantee that everything will be in place for your wedding day so that you and your beau can enjoy your special day without worrying about any of the details.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Do I Need a Wedding Planner?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'do-i-need-a-wedding-planner', '', '', '2015-03-10 12:05:25', '2015-03-10 12:05:25', '', 0, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=86', 0, 'page', '', 0),
