(92, 1, '2015-03-10 12:31:39', '2015-03-10 12:31:39', '<div class="row">\r\n        	<div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    I hired Mili 3 months before my wedding. I guess the 1 regret I have is not hiring her from the start!!! Mili was BEYOND AMAZING! I am totally type-a and would send her 1000 emails a day with all my scattered thoughts... and she would respond to EVERY SINGLE EMAIL! She would help me sort through all my wants/must-haves to get to where I really wanted to be for my wedding. Needless to say, she is incredibly patient! Also, she was great at involving my parents so that everyone''s vision was heard, and then she would find solutions on how to get me what I wanted, while respecting other people''s opinions. She was so organized throughout the planning process which was reflected on the day of! everything went off without a hitch! everyone at my wedding complimented me on how well organized the wedding was, and how everything flowed so well.</p>\r\n                    \r\n<p>I also love how she would give me her honest opinion (without being mean) when I asked for it. She has an eye for what looks good and what will work, so having her give me her true opinion, versus what I want to hear, really made decision making a lot easier as well.\r\nMoral of the Story: HIRE Planning Elegance! They are definitely worth every penny, and more!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t1.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Pooja & Shivan Desai</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: August 31, 2013</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t2.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Planning Elegance is an amazing team to work with during the tedious process of wedding planning. Mili and her team of experts were absolutely fantastic.  She was very helpful in taking over multiple tasks, including contacting my vendors and finalizing all details, helping me format the sequence of events for the reception program, providing a very detailed and organized wedding/reception timeline, and most importantly being attentive to my personal needs and making sure she always responded in a timely manner in which she ALWAYS DID! I also loved the fact that on the day of the wedding she had an assistant constantly with me and my bridesmaids and she made sure all of our needs were taken care of. Mili and her team definitely made our wedding day a very smooth and effortless process. Thank you for everything. We appreciated it! Plus, we enjoyed the marvelous shots you were able to capture</p>\r\n                    <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Maxine & Dhruv Fotadar</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: June 7, 2013</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Our daughter got married a month ago and Mili and her team helped us coordinate her 550 guest wedding as well as 350 guest henna ceremony. Many friends who attended the events have said to me that I looked so calm and happy at the wedding and that ''I'' should be a wedding coordinator, a testament to Mili''s work.</p>\r\n<p>I will admit that I was initially a bit skeptical about hiring a wedding coordinator. After all, I had done parties with several hundred people at our house so how different could a wedding be? Wrong, think again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mili was instrumental in helping me mainitain my sanity through the weding week and there were several instances where she positively saved the day. The biggest one being that when the wedding day dawned, bright and sunny, she texted me the hour-by-hour weather forecast at 7:00 a.m and even though I was hesitant she (thankfully) convinced me to move the ceremony indoors. Sure enough, it started pouring just after the barat arrived and the ceremony began!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mili is calm, pleasant, dedicated and professional. She goes the extra mile and takes care of all the detais (and there are a zillion details!) on the big day so you can relax and actually enjoy the event. I would strongly recommend her to a friend and gladly rehire her when my other kids are getting married.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t3.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Mariam & Umer Sadiq</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: December 29, 2012</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t4.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Mili and her team were absolutely incredible.  Prior to the big day, Mili was very organized and made sure to collect all the information she needed in a professional and dependable manner. She took active notes during our conversations and I could trust that every detail would be taken care of. She made the extra effort to meet me in person, and used her experience to provide guidance on how the day will flow. She definitely brought lots of excellent ideas to the table that we might not have otherwise considered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the day of the wedding, Mili and her team were 100% on. They dealt with issues, made sure all the vendors were on time, and the details were right. She made sure our families knew where they needed to be, and would have refreshments ready for them when they got there. Multiple members of my family commented on how amazing it was to have her - everyone could enjoy the festivities without a worry. It was fantastic.</p>\r\n<div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Rupa & Deepak Gupta</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: August 11, 2012</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Planning Elegance did a spectacular job with my wedding and during the months leading up to it. I worked with Mili who was an absolute pleasure. She was on point with everything, very responsive, and always had suggestions and solutions for any and all of my planning needs. On the day of my wedding, I didn''t wait longer than a blink before my needs were met. My entire family was relaxed and was able to enjoy the events to their fullest. My assigned Planning Elegance team worked tirelessly to ensure that my husband, our families, and our guests had the most memorable experience! I couldn''t speak more highly of Planning Elegance and I encourage everyone to use them. I am a very particular, type A individual, and I am still amazed at how Planning Elegance not only met my exceedingly high standards, but they surpassed them, as well.</p>\r\n                    <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Sejal & Maneesh Penkar</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: May 26, 2012</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t5.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t6.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Sejal & Arjun Makam</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: May 4, 2012</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Working with Mili was a wonderful experience. She’s friendly, easy to talk to, and most importantly, organized!  We had a wedding/reception on a larger scale at around 900 people, which was a huge undertaking for any one person to plan. She made herself available at all hours by phone and email and would even tell us when she would be out of the office at other weddings so we wouldn’t panic when we couldn''t get a hold of her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Something we valued greatly was how honest we were able to be with Mili throughout the planning process. It’s crazy to think how well Mili got to know us and there were even times where she would help us sort out our own "creative" differences. She was able to keep us on track with our budget.  Mili and her company have a lot of experience and have a great reputation in the business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it came to the day of, Mili and her team were able to make sure everything went off without a hitch. It seems like there are hundreds of different moving parts to a wedding and reception, and we couldn''t have imagined coordinating all of those things ourselves.  We highly recommend Mili and her team! Thanks so much for making our wedding events such a success!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Mili and team were absolutely wonderful! They helped us with day of coordination (which started a month prior to wedding day). They are so well prepared and kept us very close to schedule, which is a feat for Indian weddings! I didn''t have to worry about a thing the day of and I was able to enjoy everything.</p>\r\n                    <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Pinal & Keval Patel</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: March 31, 2012</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t7.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    The Planning Elegance team exhibited a level of professionalism along with a genuine concern and desire to make our event a memorable and joyous one. You were there every step of the way to ensure that we were well informed and took care of every need, big or small. God bless and thank you from the bottom of our hearts!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tesiBx1">\r\n    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n        <h4>Sana & Zubair Ziauddin</h4>\r\n        <h5>Wedding Date: June 12, 2011</h5>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Planning Elegance was our favorite and most pleasant vendor to work with. Book them ... They go above and beyond, they are very service orientated. U won''t regret it!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Planning Elegance stood out to us against other wedding planners due to their speedy, kind and personal response to our initial inquiry.  Mili is very diligent and excellent! In addition, she is very personable, understanding and compassionate. She helped recommend vendors to us without being pushy and always soothed our nerves. Mili and Amy planned detailed vendor meetings for us. We threw Mili a few last minute curve balls, and she made it happen no questions asked. We saw and spoke to Mili more than anyone else at our wedding. She is so hands on.  She tied all loose ends to make it all come together perfectly. Most importantly, guests complimented us on how professional and excellent she was!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Without a doubt Mili and her team at Planning Elegance is our number one vendor recommendation. Trust us ... She will not let you down! and it was sad to say good bye at the end. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t8.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Tulsi & Harsha Santiago</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: August 7, 2011</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Where do I start? I''m not even sure how I came across Amy, but am so lucky that I did. I had a fusion Hindu-Christian ceremony, and could not have pulled off the event without her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just a few words to describe her: Professional, Unbelievably Organized, Calming (and brides do need someone that lets them know everything will be ok) persistent in dealings with the venue and other vendors, and her follow-up is impeccable down to every spreadsheet and document she provided. She did all of this while maintaining her pleasant demeanor and shared her abundance of knowledge in wedding planning and events...well, I can go on and on, but to say Amy was a great addition to my vendors would be an understatement. She went above and beyond what I expected and handled every situation with finesse. Both families as well as myself and my groom were so happy with her and will recommend her to others without hesitation. She made the days up to the wedding run smoothly and the grand event go on without any hiccups. To say the least, she was one of my unofficial bridesmaids by the end of o