ry event while your team took care of the problems.  Anita, my MOH, couldn''t stop raving about Mili.  She loved her!  I really wish the night would have lasted longer & I could have had more time with you ladies.  I can''t wait to recommend your team to all my family & friends!  Our wedding woul dnever have been possible without Planning Elegance!!</p>\r\n <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n<div class="col-md-12 text-right paddNone">\r\n    <h4>Vaishali & Vimal Gordhan</h4>\r\n    <h5>Wedding Date: July 18, 2010</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    I just wanted to say thank you so much for all your help on the wedding day. You and your staff made the day a success. We didn''t have to worry about anything on the day of the wedding. Our moms were just sitting and relaxing before the reception. Everyone said the wedding was such a success and everything went very smoothly and we owe it to you. Thanks so much again!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tesiBx1">\r\n    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n        <h4>Amy & Nirav Desai</h4>\r\n        <h5>Wedding Date: June 19, 2010</h5>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                   So I am thoroughly convinced that the technology to clone human beings has not only been invented, it''s been perfected. Throughout the evening of our wedding there were roughly 27 Amy Patels running around with 27 clip boards and 27 wireless headsets. Sure this might sound a little crazy, but really this is the 