riends told us they really appreciated how nice and polite you were to them, and were very impressed with how professionally you coordinated both events. Thanks again for all of your help over the past several weeks, and we''ll miss working with you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                  Amy and her team were Excellent! She was always available to answer my questions and had some great ideas for layouts, visuals and finding items that worked great within my budget. She was invaluable the day of the wedding- helped set everything up and was in complete contact with the venue so that i could enjoy and get ready with my family and friends.</p>\r\n                  <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Jacque & Jeff Siegler</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: May 2, 2009</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t16.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t17.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Sapna & Ashish Patel</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: June 27, 2009</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    Dear Planning Elegance,<br>\r\nThank you so much for helping put together our dream wedding. Your team was always so professional and helpful from the very beginning and I have nothing but positive things to say! From the planned organizational meetings to the frantic day-of phone calls your team was always on top of it and managed everything in a calm collected manner. We always felt comfortable that everything was running on schedule and being taken care of, especially on the day of the wedding which was a huge relief and allowed us to actually enjoy our wedding day! I think the best part of planning elegance is their ability to customize your wedding based on your preferences, budget, culture, values, etc without forcing you in any direction. It is obvious that Planning Elegance values their clients and dedicates all the time & energy needed to get every detail perfect! Thank you again!!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                  Amy is so wonderful to work with. As all of the brides-to-be, we go through with tremendous amount of stress, worries and uncertainty. Amy was there for not only to help me with her unsurpassed services but also for mental & emotional support. She is so easy to work with she gave me the most beautiful wedding I dreamed of. Definitely will recommend her services to anyone!</p>\r\n                  <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Doris & Bill Davey</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: February 28, 2009</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t18.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-3">\r\n                <img src="[php snippet=1]/images/t19.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt=""/>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-9">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    I want to thank you for the wonderful service you provided on our wedding day. We were all very happy with how dedicated and detail-oriented you both were and how you took care of us.</p>\r\n                    <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n                    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n                    	<h4>Jinal & Rikin Patel</h4>\r\n                        <h5>Wedding Date: June 26, 2009</h5>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                   Planning Elegance - and in particular owner Amy Patel - was essential in making my wedding day an amazing success. We hired Amy about 8 months before our big day, and although our venue was already secured, she gave us great recommendations on DJ''s, decor, linens, and bridal beauty services. Amy helped us evaluate our proposals and negotiate the best price with our vendors. Her expertise in South Asian weddings and the ceremonies and unique rituals associated with them was essential. Amy is very organized and kept us on task with booking our vendors and making key decisions. On the day of, Amy and her staff kept everything running smoothly and as a result, the event was a huge success. People are still talking about our wedding almost 2 months later!</p>\r\n <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n<div class="col-md-12 text-right paddNone">\r\n    <h4>Prexa & David Graves</h4>\r\n    <h5>Wedding Date: Sept. 6, 2009</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                    THANK YOU for a beautiful job! I have certainly missed our conversations and I would not have been able to get through that weekend or my three months before it in planning without your help. I really appreciate what you have done for me and I will always keep you in mind for any one who ever wants a more than elegant wedding!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tesiBx1">\r\n    <div class="col-md-12 text-left paddNone">\r\n        <h4>Roopa & Mehul Ghandi</h4>\r\n        <h5>Wedding Date: Nov. 22, 2009</h5>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-12">\r\n            	<div class="tesiBx">\r\n                <div class="col-md-12">\r\n                	<p><i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-1x"></i>\r\n                   Sonia and I loved working with Amy. She was straight-forward and she helped us make decisions by making everything very simple and gave a ton of information about all the places to have our wedding.</p>\r\n<p>They helped me so much with my wedding! I didn''t have to lift a finger because Amy and her team were there for everything for my wedding. I would recommend them to everyone and I think all brides need a wedding planner so you can have fun at your wedding</p>\r\n <div class="tesiBx1">\r\n<div class="col-md-12 text-right paddNone">\r\n    <h4>Sonia & Raj Patel</h4>\r\n    <h5>Wedding Date: July 5, 2008</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-10 12:31:39', '2015-03-10 12:31:39', '', 29, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?p=92', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(93, 1, '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '<div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/Wedding.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">There are many low-cost or free outdoor locations to get married at. This is particularly great for summer weddings since parks, beaches, and friends’ backyards can be beautiful, free locations to recite your vows at. Historic landmarks and churches are generally low-cost venues in which you can have your wedding ceremony. You can also have your reception at a free outdoor location as long as you are willing to invest in a tent in case of adverse weather conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Wedding cakes can add up to a lot of money and bakeries often double their regular cake price just for weddings. An alternative to the traditional wedding cake can be fancy cupcakes, dessert cups, a chocolate fountain with fruit and snacks, an ice cream sundae bar, or assorted truffles. This will save you money on a cake cutting fee, which is also usually a per person fee from the venue or caterer.</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Easy Ways to Save Money on Your Wedding', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'easy-ways-to-save-money-on-your-wedding', '', '', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '', 0, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=93', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '<div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/Wedding.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">There are many low-cost or free outdoor locations to get married at. This is particularly great for summer weddings since parks, beaches, and friends’ backyards can be beautiful, free locations to recite your vows at. Historic landmarks and churches are generally low-cost venues in which you can have your wedding ceremony. You can also have your reception at a free outdoor location as long as you are willing to invest in a tent in case of adverse weather conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Wedding cakes can add up to a lot of money and bakeries often double their regular cake price just for weddings. An alternative to the traditional wedding cake can be fancy cupcakes, dessert cups, a chocolate fountain with fruit and snacks, an ice cream sundae bar, or assorted truffles. This will save you money on a cake cutting fee, which is also usually a per person fee from the venue or caterer.</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Easy Ways to Save Money on Your Wedding', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '2015-03-10 12:38:02', '', 93, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?p=94', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(95, 1, '2015-03-10 13:09:05', '2015-03-10 13:09:05', ' <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/WEDDING24.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Wedding Store 24 is fantastic store located in the heart of Little India (Artesia, CA). It was created to “provide brides with a premium wedding planning experience.” In the store, you will find an array of shelves that have different types of vendors for your wedding needs.</P>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Planning Elegance has been extremely involved with Wedding Store 24  and we are very thankful to be a part of it. They put on elaborate bridal expos that allow us to gain exposure in the South Asian Wedding industry.</p>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">It is a one-stop shop for all of your needs for your wedding day</li>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">There are 24 vendor categories with the top South Asian wedding vendors in California</li>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">There are various promotional codes with each vendor at the store to help you with your budget</li>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">It is a physical space where brides can see all of the vendors work in one trip to help save time while wedding planning</li>\r\n   <li class="wht-fnt"> Neema and her employees will give you insight on each vendor as you walk through the store with them</li>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">Through the vendor mixers that Neema graciously hosts, all of the vendors are able to build great relationships with each other which is a bonus to have them all work well on your wedding</li>\r\n    <li class="wht-fnt">Each vendor is hand picked by Wedding Store 24 and chosen to be a part of the store based on a list of stringent crtieria, so some filtering of the vendor’s quality of work has already been done for you</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">We definitely recommend that you visit the store as part of your wedding planning process!</p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>', 'Planning Elegance at Wedding Store 24', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'planning-elegance-at-wedding-store-24', '', '', '2015-03-10 13:09:05', '2015-03-10 13:09:05', '', 0, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=95', 0, 'page', '', 0);
