(99, 1, '2015-03-11 05:03:02', '2015-03-11 05:03:02', '         <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n                <img class="img-responsive" src="[php snippet=1]/images/about.jpg" alt="">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-6">\r\n				<p class="wht-fnt">Planning Elegance is a wedding coordination company that provides free wedding planning information through our wedding blogs, a friendly staff to help you with all questions, and thorough wedding planning services by professional wedding coordinators. We have experience in a multitude of different cultural events and religious weddings that tie traditional customs into modern American trends and styles. We take pride in the fact that we write all of our unique blog articles – learn more about our free wedding planning advice through our Blogger Personalities Page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">We serve all of California and specialize in (but not limited to) Los Angeles, Orange & San Diego Counties and the entire San Francisco Bay Area. If we cannot service  your area, we will guide you in the right direction for assistance. We strive to take the stress and confusion out of wedding planning process for you. Enjoy your special day without worrying. Let us Create Your Perfect Day!</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Planning Elegance takes great PRIDE in providing our clients with the best possible service through our knowledge and experience. PRIDE is our culture. The Planning Elegance mission is to always strive to meet our PRIDE principles with every single client, vendor and individual that we work with. We aim to create a lasting relationship with you to assist in creating the day of your dreams.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    <div id="portfolio">\r\n            <div class="row">\r\n                <div class="col-lg-12">\r\n                    <h2>Our Coordinators</h2>\r\n                    <hr class="star-primary">\r\n                </div>\r\n       