(378, 1, '2015-03-14 12:53:11', '2015-03-14 12:53:11', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="[php snippet=2]/about/" title="Wedding Planners">Sara Seto</a></strong><br>\r\n<strong>Dream Wedding Blogger</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I have been planning my dream wedding for as long as I can remember and I know there are many women who do the same. With tons of social media outlets now, people can spend time looking through Pinterest, Tumblr, Facebook etc. for the best wedding ideas. I will be blogging about popular wedding decoration ideas as well as other fun wedding articles and hopefully you can find something that will fit YOUR dream wedding!</p>', 'BLOGGER Sara Seto', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-sara-seto', '', '', '2015-03-14 12:53:11', '2015-03-14 12:53:11', '', 368, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=378', 0, 'page', '', 0),
