(383, 1, '2015-03-14 12:56:35', '2015-03-14 12:56:35', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="[php snippet=2]/about/" title="About">Bea Hilario</a></strong><br>\r\n<strong>Bride To Bea Blogger</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">It all comes down to the details when planning a wedding that will “wow” not only you, but also your guests. It is possible to have a unique wedding while staying true to your culture and traditions. With my blogs, I hope to inspire couples to take chances and create a wedding that will reflect both of their personalities.</p>', 'BLOGGER Bea Hilario', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-bea-hilario', '', '', '2015-03-14 13:02:40', '2015-03-14 13:02:40', '', 368, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=383', 0, 'page', '', 0),
