(386, 1, '2015-03-14 12:58:18', '2015-03-14 12:58:18', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="[php snippet=2]/about/">Cindy Boun</a><br>\r\nUniquely You Blogger</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">When it comes to planning a wedding, it is important to remember that the special day represents the love that you both share! From the trends, colors, themes, foods, etc. you choose, I hope to give you inspiring and modern ideas on how to make your wedding perfectly you. As Dr. Seuss once said, “Today you are You, that is truer than true. There is no one alive who is Youer than You.”</p>', 'BLOGGER Cindy Boun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-cindy-boun', '', '', '2015-03-14 13:02:45', '2015-03-14 13:02:45', '', 368, 'http://104.131.16.164/planningelegance/?page_id=386', 0, 'page', '', 0),
