(458, 1, '2015-03-21 07:11:08', '2015-03-21 07:11:08', '<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">November 7th, 2012 | </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-9">\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">There is so much that goes &nbsp;into a wedding, sometimes you can forget the small details such as the card box. The card box is created for your guests to be able to drop off their congratulatory wedding cards on your big day. But who would want just a plain old box when they can decorate it to fit their theme! Here are a few unique card boxes that we have seen, we hope that some of them spark your interest.</p>\r\n<h2>Bird Cage</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Since birds are trending in 2013, it is no surprise that a bird cage would make their way into card box designs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="640" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/143.jpg" title="birdcage" class="# size-full wp-image-6473"></p>\r\n<h2>House</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">A house is not a home until there is love and happiness in it. Good thing that weddings are full of both!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="823" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/144.jpg" title="house card box" class="# size-full wp-image-6474"></p>\r\n<h2>Log/Tree Stump</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">This one is great if your wedding has a nature/outdoors theme.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="742" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/145.jpg" title="log card box" class="# size-full wp-image-6475"></p>\r\n<h2>Mailbox</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Inspired by the Pixar film “Up”? Make your card box a mail box and decorate it however you see fit!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="400" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/146.jpg" title="mailbox cardbox" class="# size-full wp-image-6476"></p>\r\n<h2>Suitcase</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">This one is perfect for a destination themed wedding.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="823" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/147.jpg" title="suit case" class="# size-full wp-image-6477"></p>\r\n<h2>Treasure Chest</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">The best kind of gifts are hidden, in a treasure chest perhaps!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a target="_blank" class="pp-pinit-link" href="https://www.pinterest.com/milisweddings/"><img width="100" height="100" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/pinterest.png"></a><img width="823" height="823" alt="" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/148.jpg" title="treasure chest" class="# size-full wp-image-6478"></p>\r\n<h2>Wedding Cake</h2>\r\n<p class="wht-fnt">Whether you have a wedding cake or not, this will make for a very cute card box, but make sure you don’t mistake it for the edible wedding cake!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a targ